Package: bedcaster
Title: Bed Occupancy Forecasting for Epidemics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Finlay", "Campbell", email = "finlaycampbell93@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package for forecasting bed occupancy during epidemics using Bayesian nowcasting methods. Provides tools for data processing, delay estimation, and Stan-based modeling of ETU and isolation occupancy.
